ter controls immediately in place.\",\n2882:       \"targetBehavior\": \"The HarmonyOS route preserves the same observable behavior split: bootstrap-page @State fields update home search/filter immediately, and renderHomeRoute receives repository-backed HomePageState plus those live route-owned values on each re-render.\",\n2883:       \"verificationEvidence\": [\n2884:         \"Source review: D:/Kotlin2Cangjie/Foodike/app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/home/HomeViewModel.kt populates mutableStateOf(HomeScreenState) from repository calls and liked-restaurant collection, while HomeScreen composes from that state.\",\n2885:         \"Target review: entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj stores homeSearchQuery and homeSelectedFilter as @State and re-renders buildHomeRoute immediately on change; home_store.cj::loadHomeState supplies the repository-backed discovery state consumed by renderHomeRoute.\",\n2886:         \"Test harness blocked after compilation: 2026-06-26 reproduction of cjpm test --target aarch64-linux-ohos reached phase04_home_history_discovery_test.cj and then failed in ld.lld with missing Scrt1.o/crti.o/libm/libc, so the dedicated local-filter state test cannot yet be counted as PASS.\"\n2887:       ],\n2888:       \"parityLevel\": \"equivalent\",\n2889:       \"targetEndpoints\": [\n2890:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.homeSearchQuery\",\n2891:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.homeSelectedFilter\",\n2892:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.buildHomeRoute\",\n2893:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/home/home_store.cj::loadHomeState\",\n2894:         \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/home/home_store.cj::toggleFilter\"\n2895:       ],\n2896:       \"tests\": [\n2897:         \"entry/src/test/cangjie/phase04_home_history_discovery_test.cj::Phase04HomeHistoryDiscoveryTest.homeStoreKeepsSourceLocalFilterToggleSemantics\",\n2898:         \"entry/src/test/cangjie/phase04_home_history_discovery_test.cj::Phase04HomeHistoryDiscoveryTest.homeStoreLoadsFixtureBackedSections\"\n2899:       ],\n2900:       \"notes\": \"The target replaces Android ViewModel/State objects with route-owned @State plus a feature store, but preserves the user-visible immediate refresh semantics for phase-04 search and filter controls.\",\n2901:       \"deferredReason\": \"\",\n2902:       \"targetFallback\": \"\",\n2903:       \"risk\": \"\",\n2904:       \"futureCompletionPath\": \"\",\n2905:       \"coverageFacts\": {\n2906:         \"schemaVersion\": 1,\n2907:         \"closureKind\": \"implemented\",\n2908:         \"parityKind\": \"equivalent\",\n2909:         \"sourceBehaviorMapped\": true,\n2910:         \"targetBehaviorImplemented\": true,\n2911:         \"activeSimplification\": {\n2912:           \"used\": false,\n2913:           \"reason\": \"\",\n2914:           \"preservedBehaviors\": [],\n2915:           \"omittedBehaviors\": []\n2916:         },\n2917:         \"activeDeferred\": {\n2918:           \"used\": false,\n2919:           \"blockerKind\": \"\",\n2920:           \"blocker\": \"\",\n2921:           \"fallbackBehavior\": \"\",\n2922:           \"futureCompletionPath\": \"\"\n2923:         },\n2924:         \"verification\": {\n2925:           \"targetEndpoints\": [\n2926:             \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.homeSearchQuery\",\n2927:             \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.homeSelectedFilter\",\n2928:             \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.buildHomeRoute\",\n2929:             \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/home/home_store.cj::loadHomeState\",\n2930:             \"entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/home/home_store.cj::toggleFilter\"\n2931:           ],\n2932:           \"testEvidence\": [\n2933:             {\n2934:               \"kind\": \"harness-blocked\",\n2935:               \"detail\": \"phase04_home_history_discovery_test.cj covers local filter toggling and fixture-backed home state, but cjpm test failed during ld.lld link with missing Scrt1.o/crti.o/libm/libc.\"\n2936:             }\n2937:           ],\n2938:           \"buildEvidence\": [],\n2939:           \"runtimeEvidence\": [],\n2940:           \"manualEvidence\": [\n2941:             {\n2942:               \"kind\": \"manual-review\",\n2943:               \"detail\": \"Compared HomeViewModel/HomeScreen observable state flow with bootstrap-page @State plus home_store.cj route composition.\"\n2944:             }\n2945:           ]\n2946:         },\n2947:         \"factsSource\": \"agent\"\n\n(Showing lines 2858-2947 of 16900. Use offset=2948 to continue.)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"      \"featureId\": \"app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-home-5415bc8d6b-006-observable-state-viewmodel-flow-livedata\",\n      \"featureName\": \"Observable state, ViewModel/Flow/LiveData/recomposition, or UI state propagation.\",\n      \"sourcePath\": \"app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/home/HomeScreen.kt\",\n      \"importance\": \"critical\",\n      \"category\": \"kotlin-source\",\n      \"riskTags\": [\n        \"image_viewer\",\n        \"intent_uri\",\n        \"navigation_resource\",\n        \"permissions\",\n        \"screen_lifecycle\",\n        \"state_model\"\n      ],\n      \"keyClasses\": [],\n      \"keyMethods\": [\n        \"Home\"\n      ],\n      \"androidIds\": [],\n      \"dependencies\": [],\n      \"featurePoint\": \"Observable state, ViewModel/Flow/LiveData/recomposition, or UI state propagation.\",","truncated":true,"loaded":[]},"title":"translation-inputs\\source-cove