{"type":"text","timestamp":1782404318468,"sessionID":"ses_1007002f9ffeC2nvxFAQ5xgnmW","part":{"id":"prt_eff9360480011z5t8UvgFq8boW","messageID":"msg_eff934cd0001yvRmOI9cLMGW0a","sessionID":"ses_1007002f9ffeC2nvxFAQ5xgnmW","type":"text","text":"Repaired the bounded phase-04 group by closing the four stale `SearchBar.kt` coverage rows in the authority matrix. No target production code changes were needed because the search bar behavior was already implemented; this was an evidence/authority repair.\n\nCovered current-phase gate entries:\n- `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-compo-b7134befc8-005-data-loading-query-search-filter-or-sort`\n  SearchBar now recorded as `implemented` with precise target endpoints:\n  `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/common/widgets/search_bar.cj::renderSearchBar`\n  `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/home/home_page.cj::renderHomeRoute`\n  `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/history/history_page.cj::renderHistoryRoute`\n  `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.buildHomeRoute`\n  `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.buildHistoryRoute`\n- `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-compo-0411e44e98-004-observable-state-viewmodel-flow-livedata`\n  SearchBar state propagation now recorded as `implemented` with precise route-owned `@State` endpoints:\n  `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/common/widgets/search_bar.cj::renderSearchBar`\n  `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.homeSearchQuery`\n  `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.historySearchQuery`\n  `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.buildHomeRoute`\n  `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj::FoodikeBootstrap.buildHistoryRoute`\n- `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-compo-cd0d46a2f4-002-runtime-permission-request-permission-re`\n  Reclassified to `not-applicable` with source/target explanation that `SearchBar.kt` is only a local text-input composable and the target `renderSearchBar` has no permission-gated API usage.\n- `app-src-main-java-com-example-foodike-presentation-compo-3484491a45-003-settings-preferences-option-toggles-or-c`\n  Reclassified to `not-applicable` with source/target explanation that SearchBar has transient UI query state only, not preferences/settings behavior.\n\nRemaining current-phase gate entries:\n- None in this bounded group after the matrix repair.\n- Other phase-04 groups still have open items, but they are out of scope for this repair session.\n\nSource paths/clusters handled:\n- `app/src/main/java/com/example/foodike/presentation/components/SearchBar.kt`\n- Confirmed related target endpoints:\n  `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/common/widgets/search_bar.cj`\n  `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/app/bootstrap_page.cj`\n  `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/home/home_page.cj`\n  `entry/src/main/cangjie/ohos_app_cangjie_entry/features/history/history_page.cj`\n\nTests added or updated:\n- None.\n- I kept the existing harness-blocked situation explicit in evidence for the observable-state row. The latest workflow test report still shows `TEST_COMPILE_FAIL` due to `ld.lld` missing `Scrt1.o/crti.o/libm/libc`, so tests remain non-strong evidence here.\n\nCommands run:\n- Read/narrowing and endpoint inspection via file reads/grep\n- `C:\\Users\\Sieger\\AppData\\Local\\Programs\\Python\\Python312\\python.exe D:\\X2Cangjie\\X2Cangjie\\scripts\\shared\\source_coverage\\patch_authority.py --kind matrix --authority D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\source-coverage-matrix.json --patch D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\agent-inputs\\phase04-components-searchbar-matrix-patch.json --markdown D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\translation-inputs\\source-coverage-matrix.md --plan-json D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\plan.json --target-project D:\\workspace\\Foodike\\Foodike-Harmony`\n- `git status --short`\n\nChanged files:\n- `translation-inputs/source-coverage-matrix.json`\n  Updated the four `SearchBar.kt` rows to `implemented`/`not-applicable` with precise behavior, parity, endpoints, and verification facts.\n- `translation-inputs/source-coverage-matrix.md`\n  Synced by the authority patch tool.\n- `translation-inputs/agent-inputs/phase04-components-searchbar-matrix-patch.json`\n  Added the narrow patch payload used for the authority update.\n\nBuild result:\n- NOT RUN in this session.\n- Reused existing evidence: `translation-inputs/verification-results.md` still shows `phase-04-home-history-discovery` build gate passed.\n\nPlan changes:\n- none\n\nDeferred issues:\n- Test harness remains blocked outside this bounded group: `translation-inputs/test-build-reports/phase-03-onboarding-login-profile/test-build-report.md` still reports `ld.lld: error: cannot open Scrt1.o`.\n- The current agent brief’s expected target domain for this group is stale/incomplete because actual SearchBar behavior lives in `common/widgets/search_bar.cj` plus `bootstrap_page.cj`, not only `restaurant_card.cj`.\n\nNext recommended action:\n- Let the runner refresh phase group verdicts from the repaired matrix, then continue with the next incomplete phase-04 group, likely `presentation/history`.","time":{"start":1782404309064,"end":1782404318465}}}
